{"tid":2037450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得李嘉誠好可悲！明明咁多錢都要奶共！可憐呀！~~~","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:22:40.000Z","uid":118346,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec20939b195003539bed8a0ba00f0f4b66d358e7","tid":2037450,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"長和系創辦人李嘉誠接受「大公文匯全媒體」訪問時指，任何國家對自身國家安全問題有權責，不必過分解讀。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠又指，通過港區國安法，希望可以紓緩中央對香港的擔憂，發揮長遠穩定發展的正面作用；同時，特區政府責無旁貸，要鞏固香港人對「一國兩制」的信心，和強化國際社會的信任。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，李嘉誠日前感冒不適，身體不太舒服，因此未能及時回應媒體查詢。「今天精神稍好即馬上回覆了記者有關查詢，充分展現出一個愛國愛港商人對國家對香港義不容辭的責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1590549606855&amp;issue=20200527&amp;fbclid=IwAR1gvCh3QZ5bhHOUOo84dFx9V0wSBjOMGiB5gu3JmTJW_MIr4WZbE6KU2Q0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1590549606855%26issue%3D20200527%26fbclid%3DIwAR1gvCh3QZ5bhHOUOo84dFx9V0wSBjOMGiB5gu3JmTJW_MIr4WZbE6KU2Q0&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=76854842\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1590549606855&amp;issue=20200527&amp;fbclid=IwAR1gvCh3QZ5bhHOUOo84dFx9V0wSBjOMGiB5gu3JmTJW_MIr4WZbE6KU2Q0</a><br />\n<br />\n我做窮撚，但起碼我有獨立意志！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86af61811e325dfd5e4ebe767866b4043fbf2d8","tid":2037450,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"鍾鎮濤：「金錢破產並非末路，人格破產才是絕境。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/